text: Elena Alekseyevna Batalova () (born 27 August 1964) is a Russian freestyle skier. She won a gold medal in ski ballet at the FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships 1995 in La Clusaz. She also competed at the 1991, 1993, 1997 and 1999 world championships. == References == == External links == * Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female freestyle skiers
